The paper focuses on adaptation in robotics, specifically using a repertoire-based learning approach. This suggests that the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of planning and learning algorithms, which are common in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of simulation and evaluation of the approach on simulated tasks suggests that it could also fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions a goal-reaching task that involves avoiding obstacles, which could potentially involve computer vision techniques (cs.CV).
